      "bookmarkId": "3300076815_4_1424-1492",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "1424-1492",
      "markText": "眉为保寿官：喜清高疏秀弯长，亦宜高目一寸，尾拂天仓，主聪明富贵，机巧福寿，此保寿官成也；若粗浓黄淡，散乱低压，乃刑伤破败，此一官不成也。",
      "totalCount": 50,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300076815&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1424&rangeEnd=1492",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f2232520813ab8481g01512b?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1424&rangeEnd=1492"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300076815_5_907-956",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "907-956",
      "markText": "蜀人相眼，闽人相骨，浙人相清，淮人相重，宋人相口、江西人相色，鲁人相轩昂，胡人相鼻，太原人相重厚。",
      "totalCount": 50,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300076815&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=907&rangeEnd=956",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f2232520813ab8481g01512b?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=907&rangeEnd=956"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300076815_8_695-776",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "695-776",
      "markText": "人身具此五行，惟水火乃五行之最。水届坎居肾，肾水旺能养之肝木，木得水济而生离之心火，火得木助而生良之脾土，土得火益而生兑之肺金。此生生不息之机，乃水之化源无端也。",
      "totalCount": 48,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300076815&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=695&rangeEnd=776",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f2232520813ab8481g01512b?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=695&rangeEnd=776"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300076815_4_661-692",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "661-692",
      "markText": "面神眼神，俱如日月之明，辉辉皎皎，自然可爱，明明洁洁，久看不昏",
      "totalCount": 45,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300076815&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=661&rangeEnd=692",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f2232520813ab8481g01512b?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=661&rangeEnd=692"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300076815_4_1712-1770",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "1712-1770",
      "markText": "水耳、土耳、金耳、牛耳、圆棋耳、贴脑耳、对面不见耳，高眉一寸，轮厚廓坚，红润姿色，内有长毫，孔小不大，此采听官成也，",
      "totalCount": 42,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300076815&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1712&rangeEnd=1770",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f2232520813ab8481g01512b?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1712&rangeEnd=1770"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300076815_3_505-546",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "505-546",
      "markText": "量三停之长短，察面部之盈亏，观眉目之清秀，看神气之荣枯，取手足之厚薄，观须发之疏浊",
      "totalCount": 39,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300076815&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=505&rangeEnd=546",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f2232520813ab8481g01512b?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=505&rangeEnd=546"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300076815_4_781-835",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "781-835",
      "markText": "但人体厚者自然富贵，清者纵瘦神长，必以贵推之；浊者有神谓之厚，厚者多富；浊而无神谓之软，软者必孤，不孤则夭。",
      "totalCount": 36,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300076815&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=781&rangeEnd=835",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f2232520813ab8481g01512b?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=781&rangeEnd=835"
    },
    {
